    {"id":"n-day","category":"noun_declension","difficulty":1,"concept":"Noun — the day (f.)","en":["the day (f.)"],"gr":["η ημέρα"],"phon":["i imera"],"notes":"Feminine. η ημέρα. Καλημέρα = good day.","tags":["nouns","gender","feminine"]},

