    {"id":"n-decline-door","category":"noun_declension","difficulty":4,"concept":"Noun — Decline 'the door' (f.)","en":["the door (nom. sg.)","of the door","the door (acc.)","the doors (nom. pl.)","of the doors","the doors (acc. pl.)"],"gr":["η πόρτα","της πόρτας","την πόρτα","οι πόρτες","των πορτών","τις πόρτες"],"phon":["i porta","tis portas","tin porta","i portes","ton porton","tis portes"],"notes":"Feminine declension of -α nouns.","tags":["nouns","declension","feminine"]},
